Package: xslt
Title: Transform XML Documents with XSLT Stylesheets
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: c(person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rudis.net", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides a method to apply an XSLT stylesheet to an XML document. Based on
             the 'xmlwrapp' <http://vslavik.github.io/xmlwrapp/> C++ library.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-2
Suggests: testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: libxml2, libxslt, xmlwrapp, xsltwrapp
Imports: Rcpp, rvest, xml2, stringr, httr, stringi
